en_177431_0	It is reported that preparations are underway to use Police dogs to control protests.
en_177431_1	Director of the Police Kennel Division, SSP Lal Senevirathna said that Police Canines are currently trained for such situations with the support of Scotland Yard Police.
en_177431_2	Sri Lanka Police currently has around 160 trained dogs and are mainly deployed to raids against drug trafficking and other crimes.
